@startuml
title AllEstate App - Architecture Overview

actor "User / Client" as Client
node "Load Balancer\n(ALB)" as ALB
rectangle "ECS Cluster\n(App Tasks)" as ECS {
  component "Spring Boot App\n(REST API)" as App
  component "Payment & Billing Service\n(initiate payments, webhooks, invoices)" as Billing
  component "KYC & Provider Onboarding\n(verify providers)" as KYC
  component "Background Workers\n(indexing, thumbnails, settlements)" as Workers
}
database "RDS PostgreSQL\n(Multi-AZ)" as RDS
node "S3\n(Images & Assets)" as S3
node "OpenSearch\n(Managed)" as OS
node "AWS Secrets Manager" as Secrets
node "Payment Gateway\n(Razorpay / PayU / CCAvenue)" as PG
node "SQS\n(Async Queue)" as SQS
cloud "ECR\n(Container Registry)" as ECR
folder "Dev: docker-compose\n(Postgres + App)" as Dev

Client --> ALB : HTTPS requests (REST / Web)
ALB --> App : forwards HTTP(S)
App --> RDS : SQL (JPA / HikariCP)
App --> S3 : presigned URLs, PUT/GET for images
App --> OS : index / search (sync or async)
App --> Billing : create payment intent / invoice
Billing --> PG : create checkout / tokenization (hosted page or token API)
PG --> Client : hosted payment page / SDK (UPI, Cards, Netbanking)
PG --> Billing : webhook callback (payment success / failure)
Billing --> App : notify listing publish / change status
Billing --> RDS : write invoice, payment record
Billing --> SQS : publish 'payment_settlement' event
SQS --> Workers : consume events (async processing)
Workers --> RDS : update settlement ledger, payout status
Workers --> OS : index documents
App --> Secrets : fetch DB credentials, API keys at startup
ECR --> ECS : images pulled on deploy
Dev --> App : docker-compose for local dev (Postgres container)
App --> "CloudWatch / Logging" : logs & metrics (not shown as node)

' Sequence: Create listing with image upload

== Create listing (high level) ==
Client -> App : POST /api/listings (metadata)
App -> RDS : INSERT listing (status = DRAFT)
App -> S3 : create presigned PUT URL
App -> Client : return presigned URL
Client -> S3 : PUT image to presigned URL
Client -> App : POST /api/listings/{id}/publish
App -> RDS : verify image exists, update status = PENDING_PAYMENT
App -> Billing : create payment intent for posting (INR)
Billing -> PG : create checkout/session (hosted or token) and return client payload
Client -> PG : complete payment (UPI / Card / Netbanking / Wallet)
PG -> Billing : webhook -> payment success (signature + idempotency)
Billing -> RDS : mark listing as PAID and create invoice (GST fields)
Billing -> App : notify listing publish
Billing -> SQS : publish 'index' and 'settlement' events
SQS -> Workers : deliver events
Workers -> OS : index listing document



@enduml

